// YOUR MISSION
<p>As a pilot in [REDACTED] it is your mission to travel to the [REDACTED] in the [REDACTED] system. The only way there is through The Gates.  The Gates randomly warp you between unseen systems monitored by hostile drones. You will need to fight,  mine, trade, and fly for upgrades to survive the dangers on your way to [REDACTED].</p>
// SC-16bt Pilots Manual 
<p>Use your mouse to point your ship and hold [SPACE] to engage thrusters. Holding [SHIFT] while using your thrusters activates pulse speed enabling much faster travel speed.  If you find yourself moving too fast, hold [LEFT CTRL] to engage inertial dampeners to come to a stop. </p>
<p><em>Currently the game is in a prototype stage. Currently the game is very hard and there is not tutorial, please refer to the pilots manual above. </em><br/></p>
<p><em>Work in progress, missing lots of key pieces! Please help me improve the game, would love to hear your feedback in the comments or discussion forums.</em><br/></p>
